                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9672" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2416</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">834 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">向“阳”而生，追“光”储能——阳光电源的技术创新之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">&quot;Thriving Towards the &#39;Sun&#39;, Pursuing &#39;Light&#39; for Energy Storage - The Innovative Practice of Sungrow inCultivating New Quality Productivit</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">唐俐，陈沿江，杨舒兰，杨文亭</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">阳光电源股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">能源工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">科技发展部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">阳光电源；技术创新；新质生产力；新能源行业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Sungrow;Itechnological innovation;New quality productivity;New energy  industry</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在全球能源转型中，新能源行业迎来巨大机遇，但也面临技术快速变革的挑战。阳光电源作为新能源领军者，以技术创新为核心动力，在光伏逆变器和储能系统等领域取得显著成就。2024年，尽管众多光伏企业净利润下滑，阳光电源却保持正数，超越隆基绿能成为“光伏一哥”。本案例先追溯了阳光电源的发展历程，并深入剖析其在技术创新推进中遭遇的困境，如成本费用压力等。然后分析其面临的挑战及为应对技术创新难题所采取的措施，最后总结阳光电源技术创新对其新质生产力的提升。通过对此案例的探讨，引导学生学习并掌握技术创新相关的理论知识，思考企业在追求技术创新，应该如何采取合理的措施。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In the global energy transition, the new energy industry welcomes great opportunities, but it also faces the challenge of rapid technological change. As a leader in new energy, solar power takes technological innovation as the core power, and has made remarkable achievements in the fields of photovoltaic inverters and energy storage systems. In 2024, although the net profit of many photovoltaic enterprises declined, the solar power supply remained positive, surpassing Longji Green energy to become the &quot;photovoltaic brother&quot;. This case first traces the development process of sunshine power supply, and deeply analyzes the difficulties encountered in the promotion of technological innovation, such as cost and cost pressure. Then it analyzes the challenges and the measures taken to deal with the problem of technological innovation, and finally summarizes the improvement of the solar power technology innovation. Through the discussion of this case, we can learn and master the theoretical knowledge of technological innovation, and think about how enterprises should take reasonable measures when pursuing technological innovation and developing new quality productivity.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创新管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">技术创新驱动因素；技术创新；企业技术创新能力；产业战略性升级</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-06</td>
